Analyze Your Data

Salesforce Analytics Tools include Reports and Dashboards, Data Cloud Reports and Dashboards, CRM Analytics, Intelligent Analytics Apps, Tableau, Unified Analytics Experiences, Einstein Discovery.

To use Einstein Discovery, your org must be provisioned with an applicable license, and user accounts must be assigned the appropriate permissions. CRM Analytics Plus License and Einstein Predictions License provide access to Einstein Discovery.

CRM Analytics Plus Admin provides admin-level access to all Einstein Discovery features, while CRM Analytics Plus User provides restricted access to models. Einstein Discovery in Tableau License gives users access to predictions and improvements only.

To learn more, see Assign Einstein Discovery Permission Sets to Users or Einstein Discovery Capacities and Requirements.
title: Einstein Discovery License and Permissions Requirements
